nter). \n\n\u2022  Do not check services that were provided solely in conjunction with a surgical procedure or diagnostic \n\nprocedure, such as IV medications. Surgical procedures include routine pre- and post-operative \n\n\u2022  procedures. \n\n\u2022  For O0110A1 (Chemotherapy), O0110B1 (Radiation), and O0110J1 (Dialysis), check if the patient is \n\nundergoing treatment at the time of assessment. \n\nCoding Instructions", "type": "Document"}}